**Overview**
This dashboard provides an overview of the Audit Event detected by the Canva.
This dashboard use Bar Charts to display Target name, Context IP and Top Teams across the Audit Event. Pie Chart displays the Outcome Result, Approval Status, and Actor Type distribution. The dashboard also showcase the Top 10 Actor User, Action User, and Target User Information over the Event. A Pie Chart also exist to provide information related to event by the Action Type. Line Chart displays the event distribution over time.
